sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant S as Scraper
    participant E as Emailer
    participant Sch as Scheduler
    participant L as Logger
    M->>S: create Scraper
    M->>E: create Emailer
    M->>L: create Logger
    M->>Sch: create Scheduler
    Sch->>S: schedule scrape
    S->>E: send news
    E->>L: log errors
    Sch->>M: end program
